**********************************************************************************

NOTE: Currently Apache 2.0.x, IIS 6.0, IIS 7.0, Webserver 7.0 and Proxyserver 4.0 Agent 
have Agent 3.0 features enabled. Also this is the only agent that users can build and install
(Webserver 7.0 agent is supported platforms are Solaris sparc, Solaris x86 and
RHAS Linux 4.0, 5.0 and Windows 2003 and Proxyserver 4.0 Agent is supported onlyonly on Solaris sparc)
Rest of the Agents for other containers viz. Sharepoint and OWA agents are 
yet to have the Agent 3.0 features enabled. They will be done in a timely manner.

If you would like to build any other agent, please use 2.2 agents 
from opensso branch. Opensso branch details:
cvs -d :pserver:username@cvs.dev.java.net:/cvs co -r opensso_agent22_branch opensso

Nightly and stable builds are available on opensso web site.

***********************************************************************************

